title: Close to Grocery Stores, Restaurants, Coffee Shops & More!
posting_body: ['The Legends of Champlin is Champlin, Minnesota’s all-new, premier 55+ independent living senior community!', 'We have paid attention to every detail and are offering smart layouts, quality materials, and luxurious amenities seldom found in this price range.', 'Enjoy the comforts of maintenance-free living along with the convenience of an outstanding location.', 'These one, two and three bedrooms feature granite kitchen counters, a private balcony or patio (most homes), and a full-size washer and driver in every unit.', 'The community amenities are also perfect for hosting the grandkids and other special events!', 'Reserve your new home today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Close to Grocery Stores, Restaurants, Coffee Shops & More!', '- Professional On-Site Management Team', '- Cards & Crafts Room', '- Large Walk-In Closet(s)', '- Pet-Friendly Community', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Champlin is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Champlin', '11635 Theatre Drive', 'Champlin, MN, 55316', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'EGT6aq5r0az']
